Package: sys
Type: Package
Title: Portable System Utilities
Version: 0.1
Author: Jeroen Ooms
Maintainer: Jeroen Ooms <jeroen.ooms@stat.ucla.edu>
Description: Powerful replacements for base system2 with consistent behavior across
